@BASE_URL = http://localhost:3000
@USER_TOKEN = 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
@GROUP_ID = 1
@PLAYER_ID = 10

### Listar Grupos
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

### Criar Grupo
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Melhores 2025",
  "description": "XI principal",
  "competition": "PL",
  "year": 2025
}

### Detalhes do Grupo
GET {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups/{{GROUP_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

### Atualizar Grupo (name/description)
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups/{{GROUP_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Melhores 2025 - edit",
  "description": "Atualizado"
}

### Apagar Grupo
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups/{{GROUP_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}

### Adicionar Jogador ao Grupo (máx. 11)
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups/{{GROUP_ID}}/players
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "{{PLAYER_ID}}",
  "playerName": "John Doe",
  "teamCode": "MCI",
  "teamName": "Manchester City"
}

### Remover Jogador do Grupo
DELETE {{BASE_URL}}/api/groups/{{GROUP_ID}}/players/{{PLAYER_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{USER_TOKEN}}
